  "text": "Guo et al, 2011 [CITATION_1] Experimental study. Animals divided into groups with biliary cirrhosis induced by bile duct ligation and sham. Expression of heme oxygenase-1 in kidneys was analyzed as serum creatinine and renal blood flow.",
